Barbed arrows are a special set of arrows obtained from the Attacker dispenser during a game of Barbarian Assault. It is only obtainable by players if they are assigned the Attacker role, and are used to harm Penance Fighters and Rangers when they are weak to the Defensive/Barbed/Fire styles, which the Collector will call.

The feather's colours match the colour of the magic spell element that the fighters and rangers are weak to, which makes it easy to know which arrow should be equipped once the Collector has made the correct call.

'''Barbed arrows''' are a special set of arrows obtained from the Attacker dispenser during a game of [[Barbarian Assault]]. It is only obtainable by players if they are assigned the Attacker role, and are used to harm [[Penance Fighter]]s and [[Penance Ranger|Rangers]] when they are weak to the ''Defensive/Barbed/Fire'' styles, which the Collector will call.

The feather's colours match the colour of the magic spell element that the fighters and rangers are weak to, which makes it easy to know which arrow should be equipped once the Collector has made the correct call.
